OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSkies
OL,6,Fbecoming rather cloudy as a band of
OL,7,Frain moves eastwards this evening, but
OL,8,Fweakening before reaching some eastern
OL,9,Fareas. Turning milder but increasingly
OL,10,Fwindy overnight, with another band of
OL,11,Frain reaching the far west later.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSunday:FRain and brisk winds will move
OL,14,Fnortheast through the morning. Drier
OL,15,Fwith perhaps some brightness across
OL,16,Fsome southern and central areas during
OL,17,Fthe afternoon. Feeling milder for all.
